title: Frankenstein - Radio Adaptation
description:
2 X 60 mins

We've all seen the films, so now hear the original story. Gone is the Gothic castle, peasants with burning staves and the mysterious "mittle European" setting. This tale is darker, Frankenstein much more a well meaning but troubled young man. The story ranges from Switzerland, through the Orkneys to the north of Scotland to the Arctic ice, with many a murder en route.
